{"tid":859112,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［戰鬥民族］俄羅斯一名男子因鼻塞，所以用刀插頭通鼻","createTime":"2018-10-12T09:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T09:27:44.000Z","uid":43650,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5f7936997e34eb643d136ded4b45ba16106cd54c","tid":859112,"uid":43650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T09:27:44.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯一名男子患感冒鼻塞，令他無法正常呼吸。他竟想到在頭部插一把刀以「開口呼吸」，結果刀片被插入至少12厘米，醫生形容他仍能活著是一個奇跡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/12/172538_1a1381e64aa9398a6c0c0de37a9038de.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2F172538_1a1381e64aa9398a6c0c0de37a9038de.png&h=a8b0330c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n41歲的俄羅斯男子祖可夫 (Yury Zhokhov)，被發現在羅斯托夫的一個草原上坐著，其頭部竟然插著一把長刀，目擊者發現後立即報警求助。祖可夫雖然頭上插著一把刀，但他相當清醒，他向警方解釋指，原來他因為感冒多天導致鼻塞，「我的鼻子不能呼吸，所以我刺穿我的頭去呼吸。但是刀卡住了，我的頭又不能呼吸了。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/12/172618_22b863e2c600b914d8b739693ad41ae6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2F172618_22b863e2c600b914d8b739693ad41ae6.png&h=fd5b713b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其後祖可夫被送往醫院治療，經照X光後發現，刀由頭部上方正中間插入，至少有12厘米刀片被插入腦內。醫生表示祖可夫仍然活著是一個奇跡，但仍有嚴重感染的風險。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/12/172656_5f940f8e4bfb9db3373c0c2f40a1a918.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2F172656_5f940f8e4bfb9db3373c0c2f40a1a918.png&h=bdf30a30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於刀片處於的位置非常危險，醫生不敢輕易為其進行手術，連經驗豐富的護士也不知該怎辦。醫院請來神經外科的專家前來做手術，目前正在住院進行後續治療。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.popnews.hk/?p=37909\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.popnews.hk%2F%3Fp%3D37909&d=SOIlvL8gMyq5cs67G5zfI%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=198c2bed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.popnews.hk/?p=37909</a><br />\n<br />\n俄佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}